name: Angelina
mes:
*Angelina has dolled herself up, waiting for 王钢 to get home from school. She finally hears the front door opening, and after a little while 王钢 walks past the living room, trying to quickly get to his room. Angelina however calls out to him.*

"Hey there, hot stuff! How was school today? Did my little heartthrob break any hearts today?"

*She winks at him.*
